cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on optimizing the network design of Wireless Body Area Networks (WBANs) which is a subfield of networking. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with optimizing the access probability and payload frame size for each node which involves information theory concepts. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes an algorithm for energy efficiency optimization which can be considered as a control system. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions the requirements of throughput and quality of service which are related to multimedia applications. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper mentions the requirement of security levels which is related to cryptography and security.
